name: ShipFall (shaen)
description:
ShipFall is a brand-new Space exploration game! Locate Earth in this HUGE galaxy, re-fueling and rebuilding your spacecraft from materials of distant planets. Some Alien life exist on these planets, so watch out, and execute them before they kill you and your mission!

Controls:

Bot: 

WASD - Movement

Click - Mine & Attack

Player: A & D & Space - Movement
